      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HEAD KAHUNA (5) two-start gelding resuming. Has shown enough at both starts and finds a winnable contest to kick off his third prep. Sharpened for this with a 900m trial placing at Scone. Go close. RAYGUN ROCKS (10) returns from a  lengthy spell. Drawn out in her two career starts and today is no different. Was a month between runs when she went back from the gate to finish eighth to Beadman over 1250m at Newcastle last April. Can measure up at the first run for a new barn. HANUMAN (1) heavily supported at his first run for the new yard with a fading fifth over 1100m at Dubbo. Deserves another chance with a host of gear changes. HARRY (2) resuming from a spell. Placed in a recent Scone trial. Raced just once last campaign and finished eighth at Dubbo over 1000m. May need the run but monitor the market.",
